        },
        "subject": "LU-3765 open: simplify open_by_fid",
        "message": "LU-3765 open: simplify open_by_fid\n\nOnce client specified MDS_OPEN_BY_FID, mds should never try open\nwith name because name may be invalid, and even it's valid, it\nmay cause inconsistency.\n\nPack name for intent open for backward compatibility with 2.1\nserver.\n\nSigned-off-by: Lai Siyao <lai.siyao@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I95f856f5ac7ac0264e321eb97e8015dab2d106bf\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_4"
    }
